data.description: Welcome home to the community of Laurel Vista with the community pool a few steps from your home! Walk inside and you have a flex room that can be used as an office area or dining room, kitchen is bright with white cabinets, tiled backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Family room is spacious and has room off the kitchen for breakfast table. Family room is full of natural light with many windows. Primary bedroom is downstairs with a walk in closet and full bathroom. Laundry room and a half bath are downstairs as well. Upstairs you will find so much room for additional living. Huge game room at the top of the stairs that splits the bedrooms apart for privacy. 2 nice size bedrooms that share a jack and jill bathroom are on both sides of the game room that also has a nice walk in closet. 4 rooms total upstairs with 2 full baths. This home offers so much space and flexibility. Outside you will appreciate the oversized concrete slab that is perfect for outdoor entertaining. There is also an additional concrete slab for a basket ball hoop, or a storage unit. Fence is stained and has solar panel lights for night time glow.  Ceiling fans in all bedrooms, added insulation in the attic, Water softener, epoxy in garage. Community is minutes from school in the community, shopping, dining, 1604 and HWY 90. A quick commute to Lackland AFB, Toyota and Hwy 151.
